{
  "stem": "7598.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My maternal grandfather came earlier and became a very wealthy diamond merchant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Unfortunately, he lost a lot of money during the First World War.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father started-- my father had been schooled in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He left school at the age of 13, but he was really-- he should have been an academic, which is probably why my brother and my son became one.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But unfortunately, he left school at the age of 18.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he still quoted Latin just before he died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he started working as a diamond cleaver, which is some sort of diamond cutter, and eventually became a diamond merchant.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by the time I was born, my brother were born, we were-- they were comfortable, middle-class business people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My four grandparents lived in Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're all actually in the family plan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was one of six, and my mother, I think, was one of six.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were, we were secular Jews, but we were very Jewish-orientated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think by the fact that the diamond community was a very small and a very close community, one was very much that way orientated.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were secular Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father was very good towards other people and helped both his ugly younger sisters to get married.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we weren't designed as family, not in the sort of [NON-ENGLISH] manner.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father used to say that it's the duty of a Jew to give money to another Jew to send a third Jew to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We both went to a private school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The main reason is that Antwerp was beginning to be Flemish-orientated, and my parents wanted us brought up in French.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a very liberal school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a lot of the teachers--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
